{"tid":1502212,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"原來有方法叫美國取消支那留學生簽證","createTime":"2019-08-24T15:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T08:29:39.000Z","uid":134134,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f9742795bb9c4080a3e13c1fa4300291611db241","tid":1502212,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:17:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係聯署啦！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【現存白宮聯署更新】<br />\n<br />\n明白現在實在太多白宮聯署，好多人會唔記得自己簽咗邊個，我有以下建議：<br />\n<br />\n1/ 唔肯定嘅，簽多一次。在我的道德標準下，呢個可以，因為你唔係故意用同一個電郵簽幾次。<br />\n<br />\n2/ 簽咗之後，自己mark返自己簽咗邊個，這是大家的責任。<br />\n<br />\n《未夠數》<br />\n==========<br />\n中國武警冒充香港警察，白宮聯署請求美國國會盡快通過香港人權民主法案 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YW8pa8&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=5026f7e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國取消中國學生簽證<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30GcBMM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30GcBMM&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=6aba1f2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30GcBMM</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國派美軍拯救香港巿民<br />\n <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KsmYOQ&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=e12e7d50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國將中國共產黨定性為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MlpLM3&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=f2f3ad15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國向北京施壓，停止製造白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Zkc8hX&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=8372aef6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX</a><br />\n<br />\n拯救國泰航空，保障經濟自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZmWgPU&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=14c73260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU</a><br />\n<br />\n要求拒絕前警務處處長曾偉雄到聯合國就任提名<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Z0cMkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Z0cMkw&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=97969988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Z0cMkw</a><br />\n<br />\n🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n《以下夠數，但到期前越多人越好》<br />\n==========<br />\n請求美國派出醫療船支援香港 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2H221Iu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H221Iu&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=c3772146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2H221Iu</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國國會確認香港警察為恐怖組織 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KzVVQB&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=b70703c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB</a><br />\n<br />\n請美國國會提名【爭取民主自由的香港人】競逐諾貝爾和平獎，藉以保護義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZbGdQH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZbGdQH&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=3a105703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZbGdQH</a><br />\n<br />\n簽名＞等電郵＞確認簽名＞傳開去<br />\n<br />\n來自：Is But 是但哥 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/isbutbrother/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fisbutbrother%2F&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=9fc12f26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/isbutbrother/</a>"},{"pid":"64134a3f8b676ddffa0d6184078509c8062979dd","tid":1502212,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:18:13.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid